# Title: Potential Password Spraying Attempt Using Dsacls.EXE
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-06-20
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects possible password spraying attempts using Dsacls
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1218
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_dsacls_password_spray.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Legitimate use of dsacls to bind to an LDAP session

CommandLine="*/user:*" CommandLine="*/passwd:*" Image="*\\dsacls.exe" OR OriginalFileName="DSACLS.EXE"